{"tid":2245302,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"不換肩：把全部心思和精力放在備戰打仗","createTime":"2020-10-16T06:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T06:31:59.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2db12dbd7b8cea433fef8611b23103e64670cdaa","tid":2245302,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:21:55.000Z","msg":"中國東部戰區表示，昨日（14日）一艘美國「巴里號」驅逐艦穿航台灣海峽，解放軍東部戰區組織海空兵力全程對美艦進行跟蹤監視。<br />\n<br />\n東部戰區的官方微信週四稱，近來，美國在涉台問題上頻頻向台灣獨發出「錯誤信號」，嚴重破壞台海地區和平穩定。並呼籲美方停止在台海地區「滋事攪局」的言行。<br />\n<br />\n台灣國防部早前表示，週三有一艘美國驅逐艦由南向北航經台灣海峽後，續往北行駛。國防部指出，台方對美艦經台灣海峽北駛期間均全程掌握，周邊海、空域相關動態，狀況均正常。<br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平週二視察海軍陸戰隊時曾指出要「加快提升作戰能力」，「努力鍛造一支合成多能、快速反應、全域運用的精兵勁旅」，「要把全部心思和精力放在備戰打仗上，保持高度戒備狀態」。<br />\n<br />\n編：Perry<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：香港電台"},{"pid":"f78319dd360ab3f4691148b17a05be28c416eac5","tid":2245302,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/121244591_221514825976542_4769162718230209481_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=9e2e56&amp;_nc_ohc=Ns-akVKJr08AX81rySZ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=c75a0431cb63ffd92586887419bb1b86&amp;oe=5FAD45A5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F121244591_221514825976542_4769162718230209481_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D9e2e56%26_nc_ohc%3DNs-akVKJr08AX81rySZ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26tp%3D6%26oh%3Dc75a0431cb63ffd92586887419bb1b86%26oe%3D5FAD45A5&h=52f34afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMAruJN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMAruJN.jpg&h=a8ef09be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fbcbefad3d56124cbe1c903b959d2ec93d38a0f","tid":2245302,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"講就唔會做，做就唔會講"},{"pid":"96ca4511d275b86340f374a3cec5820eeec3912d","tid":2245302,"uid":292